Early Computing
From this video i've learned the very first thing for Computing was the abacus made 2500 BCE.
It was a hand operated calculator that the people in that time add and subtract multiple numbers. It
also stored the state of Computation sorta like todays storing system. later after that used clocks or
ruler to calculate the sunrise, tide, time and bodys of water(sea). The Step Reckoner was also one 
of kind Computing but machine that was automated and can do most of the things before from past create
objects for computing.

